changelog.info:
- Switch to user build
- Updated OnePlus Camera, blobs, ODM features & CarrierConfig from OnePlus 9R OOS 11.4.5.5
- Fixed NightScape mode green shade issue on OnePlus Camera
- Fixed Crackling Sound issue on voice call at high volume and improved audio
- DeviceSettings: Added back OnePlus Dolby & QS tile (Disable by default)
- DeviceSettings: Added GameMode toggle & QS tile
- DeviceSettings: Update icons & Minor improvements
- DeviceSettings: Drop KCAL settings
- Touch: Reorder gesture keys (Avoid original gestures invalid after flashing a custom kernel which doesn't support new gestures)
- Added keyboard padding props from stock
- Fixed Live Caption button position on landscape mode
- overlay: Dropped Havoc FOD Icon
- overlay: Don't pin camera app in memory
- rootdir: Added back init.cust.rc
- rootdir: Force DSDS rather than SSSS
- Updated Authsecret, CDSP, Configstore, Gatekeeper, Graphics, IO prefetcher, IRQ balance, Keymaster, Peripheral manager, Perf, Snapdragon Computer Vision Engine, Soter, Thermal engine, Time services, Trusted User Interface and VPP blobs from LA.UM.9.12.r1-11500-SMxx50.0
- kernel: Rebranded perf to Havoc-sm8250
- kernel: Merged 'LA.UM.9.12.r1-12800-SMxx50.0' CAF tag
- kernel: power: supply: Fix kernel building without mp2650 driver
- kernel: dtsi: fix duplicate overlays
- kernel: power: Silence debug logging
- kernel: configs: Enable wireguard
- Other minor cleanup & improvements
